title: Alone in the Dark 3 playthrough
description: This game is uhh... really bizarre. The more I think about it the more I think it's actually the worst of the original 3. 1 is great obviously, and 2 is fuckin weird and dumb but at least it's kind of charming, and the pirate setting is fun. This one is just annoying.
